amendment.description: Page 334, line 23, insert before the colon the following: ``and that the new Government of Egypt fulfills its commitment to the Egypt-Israel Peace Treaty signed on March 26, 1979, and to freedom of navigation of the Suez Canal''.
amendment.purpose: An amendment numbered 481 printed in the Congressional Record to add language to Egypt on fulfilling the Egypt-Israel Treaty.

action.text: By unanimous consent, the Franks (AZ) amendment was withdrawn.
House amendment offered/reported by: Amendment (A063) offered by Mr. Franks (AZ).
